<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">wagon</ENAMEX>. It's deeper poverty.

            <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">Third</NUMEX>,
even leaving lofty universalism aside, international trade <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organizations</ENAMEX> can
help promote a liberal agenda domestically. In <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Britain</ENAMEX> the left supports the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">European Union</ENAMEX> and the right doesn't. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</NUMEX> reason is that the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">EU</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">meddles</ENAMEX> in
