regulation. Yet many of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">today</TIMEX>'s progressives are economic <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">nationalists</ENAMEX>, viewing
unilateral tariffs as the policy tool of choice.

            
Evolutionary psychology tells us that economic
