economic activity is essentially a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">force</ENAMEX> of nature--it can be guided, it can be
slowed, but it can't, realistically, be stopped. The original progressives
chose to swim with this basic current of history. Many of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">today</TIMEX>'s
"progressives" are swimming against it.

